Assemble the Structure Outline draft. Format:

```md
## Structure Outline

**Shape**: {{shape_mode}} {{if recipe-driven: "(tag recipe: {{primary_tag}})"}}
**Parts**: {{use_parts ? "Yes — section grouping for batched review" : "No — flat section list"}}

### Sections

{{if use_parts:}}
**Part 1: {{part_1.title}}**
1. {{section_name}} — {{one-line scope}}
2. ...

**Part 2: {{part_2.title}}**
...
{{else:}}
1. {{section_name}} — {{one-line scope}}
2. ...
{{end}}

### Custom additions

{{list of custom_additions with rationale, or "(none)" if recipe-driven and not customized}}

### Recipe omissions

{{list of custom_omissions with rationale, or "(none)"}}
```

Store as {{structure_outline_draft}}.

